{"type":"message","id":"0ef3ab40","parentId":"80c7ee17","timestamp":"2026-04-11T09:01:21.270Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问都有什么技能，我已经列出了框架内置技能（部分）和工作区技能。现在我需要整理一下，做个简洁的分类呈现给用户。框架内置技能主要是和外部服务/工具的集成，工作区技能主要是工作流相关的自定义技能。可以按类别简单说明。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n当前可用技能：\n\n### 框架内置技能（~55个）\n涵盖外部服务集成：\n- **通讯**：discord, imsg, apple-messages\n- **笔记/文档**：notion, obsidian, bear-notes, apple-notes, 1password\n- **代码/开发**：github, gh-issues, coding-agent, claude-code-*\n- **搜索/数据**：web-search, multi-search-engine, gemini\n- **生活**：weather, blucli, gog, goplaces, himalaya\n\n### 工作区自定义技能（~30个）\n主要是本地扩展：\n- **任务编排**：task-orchestrator-v7, task_orchestrator, v8_classifier, v8_scorer\n- **记忆系统**：elite-longterm-memory, memory-keeper, ontology, proactivity\n- **自动化**：automation-workflows, productivity-automation-kit, vercel-deploy\n- **开发工具**：github-manager, scrapling, skill-vetter, self-improving\n- **安全拦截**：critical-interceptor, scene-classifier\n\n---\n\n完整列表可通过 `ls ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/` 和 `ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` 查看。需要了解某个具体技能的用法吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":27738,"output":327,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28065,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775898074883,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1f4a0956-33f0-4471-8039-14350f5f585b"}}
